# MDX Heading Style

Do not use inline code marks in Markdown headings.

Bad:

```mdx
## Tailwind `dark:` variant
## Polymorphic `render`
### Custom elements with `render`
```

Good:

```mdx
## Tailwind dark variant
## Polymorphic render
### Custom elements with render
```

Keep code formatting in the body content immediately below the heading when the exact symbol matters.
